{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/bibliotecas-com-cocoapods/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Felipe Mendes"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"caa86984-13a5-5f45-ab4b-5581d14f14ab","excerpt":"A maioria das linguagens modernas possuem soluções para distribuição de código. Por exemplo, JavaScript tem o NPM, PHP o Composer, .NET o Nuget, entre outras…","html":"<p>A maioria das linguagens modernas possuem soluções para distribuição de código. Por exemplo, JavaScript tem o <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/\">NPM</a>, PHP o <a href=\"https://getcomposer.org/\">Composer</a>, .NET o <a href=\"https://getcomposer.org/\">Nuget</a>, entre outras. Em iOS não é diferente, a Apple possui o próprio gerenciador de tarefas chamado <a href=\"https://swift.org/package-manager/\">Swift Package Manager</a> para compartilhar e distribuir pacotes em Swift. Porém este não é muito utilizado ainda por grande parte dos desenvolvedores. A maioria opta por outros gerenciadores de tarefas não oficiais da Apple que são <a href=\"https://cocoapods.org/\">CocoaPods</a> e <a href=\"https://github.com/Carthage/Carthage\">Carthage</a>, ambos open source.</p>\n<p>Visto que estes são mais utilizados irei detalhar como é a criação e distribuição de uma biblioteca utilizando <em>CocoaPods</em>. O exemplo utilizado para estudo será uma <em>lib</em> que criptografa textos que irei chamar de <em>iHash</em>. O projeto final pode ser encontrado no <a href=\"https://github.com/felipemendes/iHash\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2>Criando a biblioteca</h2>\n<p>Bibliotecas do CocoaPods utilizam o tipo <em>Cocoa Touch Framework</em>, portanto basta iniciar um novo projeto no <em>Xcode</em> com este template selecionado.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ac788bdb63786fc5cae4c72cf218162e/203d3/cocoa-touch-framework.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.291139240506325%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Cocoa Touch Framework\"\n        title=\"Cocoa Touch Framework\"\n        src=\"/static/ac788bdb63786fc5cae4c72cf218162e/f058b/cocoa-touch-framework.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ac788bdb63786fc5cae4c72cf218162e/c26ae/cocoa-touch-framework.png 158w,\n/static/ac788bdb63786fc5cae4c72cf218162e/6bdcf/cocoa-touch-framework.png 315w,\n/static/ac788bdb63786fc5cae4c72cf218162e/f058b/cocoa-touch-framework.png 630w,\n/static/ac788bdb63786fc5cae4c72cf218162e/40601/cocoa-touch-framework.png 945w,\n/static/ac788bdb63786fc5cae4c72cf218162e/78612/cocoa-touch-framework.png 1260w,\n/static/ac788bdb63786fc5cae4c72cf218162e/203d3/cocoa-touch-framework.png 1322w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Certifique-se que o checkbox <em>Include Unit Tests</em> esteja marcado para aplicarmos os testes unitários no projeto.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/198353dd773f8f3ba89fd9d65c861256/203d3/include-unit-tests.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.291139240506325%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Include Unit Tests\"\n        title=\"Include Unit Tests\"\n        src=\"/static/198353dd773f8f3ba89fd9d65c861256/f058b/include-unit-tests.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/198353dd773f8f3ba89fd9d65c861256/c26ae/include-unit-tests.png 158w,\n/static/198353dd773f8f3ba89fd9d65c861256/6bdcf/include-unit-tests.png 315w,\n/static/198353dd773f8f3ba89fd9d65c861256/f058b/include-unit-tests.png 630w,\n/static/198353dd773f8f3ba89fd9d65c861256/40601/include-unit-tests.png 945w,\n/static/198353dd773f8f3ba89fd9d65c861256/78612/include-unit-tests.png 1260w,\n/static/198353dd773f8f3ba89fd9d65c861256/203d3/include-unit-tests.png 1322w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Crie um novo arquivo <em>.swift</em> com o nome <em>iHash</em> dentro do target de mesmo nome. Este arquivo irá conter o comportamento básico da biblioteca. O comportamento é muito simple e possui apenas uma função para gerar o valor <em>MD5</em> de uma <em>string</em> informada.</p>\n<p>Conteúdo do arquivo <em>iHash.swift</em>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Foundation</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CommonCrypto</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">final</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> iHash <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    \n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">md5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token omit keyword\">_</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-></span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> length <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>CC_MD5_DIGEST_LENGTH<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> digest <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token class-name\">UInt8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>repeating<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> count<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        \n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> d <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">data</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>using<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Encoding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>utf8<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token omit keyword\">_</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>withUnsafeBytes <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">UnsafePointer</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">UInt8</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span>\n                <span class=\"token function\">CC_MD5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">CC_LONG</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>digest<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        \n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token operator\">..&lt;</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">reduce</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token short-argument\">$0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>format<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"%02x\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> digest<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token short-argument\">$1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>A estrutura do projeto e o conteúdo do arquivo deverá ficar dessa forma:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/77fa4a973e2b7abc16461b865b8924a1/d5bfb/iHash.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.39240506329114%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"iHash\"\n        title=\"iHash\"\n        src=\"/static/77fa4a973e2b7abc16461b865b8924a1/f058b/iHash.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/77fa4a973e2b7abc16461b865b8924a1/c26ae/iHash.png 158w,\n/static/77fa4a973e2b7abc16461b865b8924a1/6bdcf/iHash.png 315w,\n/static/77fa4a973e2b7abc16461b865b8924a1/f058b/iHash.png 630w,\n/static/77fa4a973e2b7abc16461b865b8924a1/40601/iHash.png 945w,\n/static/77fa4a973e2b7abc16461b865b8924a1/d5bfb/iHash.png 1072w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Criando o teste unitário</h2>\n<p>Teste de unidade é muito importante para manter o funcinamento ideal da aplicação. Portanto, vamos utilizá-lo para validar o comportamento da nossa biblioteca. No arquivo <code class=\"language-text\">iHashTests.swift</code> altere a classe com o seguinte código para testar o nosso método <code class=\"language-text\">md5()</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\"><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ihash<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> iHash<span class=\"token operator\">!</span>\n    \n<span class=\"token keyword\">override</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">setUp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    ihash <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">iHash</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"token function-definition function\">testMD5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> test<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"testing\"</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token class-name\">XCTAssertEqual</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ihash<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">md5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>test<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string-literal\"><span class=\"token string\">\"ae2b1fca515949e5d54fb22b8ed95575\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Ao executar o teste a validação deve passar e será exibido um resumo dos métodos verificados.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/343f9489d5a88d606ba663e637bef942/f43e4/teste-unitario.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.291139240506325%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Teste unitário\"\n        title=\"Teste unitário\"\n        src=\"/static/343f9489d5a88d606ba663e637bef942/f058b/teste-unitario.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/343f9489d5a88d606ba663e637bef942/c26ae/teste-unitario.png 158w,\n/static/343f9489d5a88d606ba663e637bef942/6bdcf/teste-unitario.png 315w,\n/static/343f9489d5a88d606ba663e637bef942/f058b/teste-unitario.png 630w,\n/static/343f9489d5a88d606ba663e637bef942/40601/teste-unitario.png 945w,\n/static/343f9489d5a88d606ba663e637bef942/f43e4/teste-unitario.png 1120w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Publicando a biblioteca</h2>\n<p>Finalizado o comportamento básico da biblioteca é hora de publicá-la direto no <a href=\"https://cocoapods.org/.\">CocoaPods</a>. Instale o <code class=\"language-text\">cocoapods</code> pelo terminal:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\">$ gem install cocoapods</code></pre></div>\n<p>Adicione o arquivo <code class=\"language-text\">podspec</code>. Esse arquivo é responsável por armezenar o nome, descrição, versão e informações essenciais do <code class=\"language-text\">pod</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"swift\"><pre class=\"language-swift\"><code class=\"language-swift\">$ pod spec create iHash</code></pre></div>\n<p>O arquivo <code class=\"language-text\">iHash.podspec</code> será criado na raiz do projeto. Altere com informações conforme o modelo a seguir:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">Pod::Spec.new do |spec|\n\n  spec.name         = \"iHash\"\n  spec.version      = \"0.0.1\"\n  spec.summary      = \"Lib that generates hash values\"\n\n  spec.description  = &lt;&lt;-DESC\nA CocoaPods library that generates hash values\n                   DESC\n\n  spec.homepage     = \"https://github.com/felipemendes/iHash\"\n  spec.license      = { :type => \"MIT\", :file => \"LICENSE\" }\n  spec.author       = { \"felipemendes\" => \"felipemendes@me.com\" }\n\n  spec.ios.deployment_target = \"12.1\"\n  spec.swift_version = \"4.2\"\n\n  spec.source        = { :git => \"https://github.com/felipemendes/iHash.git\", :tag => \"#{spec.version}\" }\n  spec.source_files  = \"iHash/**/*.{h,m,swift}\"\n\nend</code></pre></div>\n<p>Para validar se as informações desse arquivo estão corretas podemos executar o comando:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ pod lib lint</code></pre></div>\n<p>Visto que utilizei o GitHub para armazenar o código e facilitar o vínculo com o CocoaPods, é necessário criar uma <code class=\"language-text\">tag</code> no repositório para distribuir o <code class=\"language-text\">pod</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ git tag 0.0.1\n$ git push origin 0.0.1</code></pre></div>\n<p>Feito isso basta enviar o <code class=\"language-text\">pod</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ pod trunk push</code></pre></div>\n<p>Link para o projeto final no <a href=\"https://github.com/felipemendes/iHash\">GitHub</a>.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Bibliotecas com CocoaPods","date":"28 março, 2019","description":""}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/gerenciamento-de-memoria/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Gerenciamento de Memória"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/xcode-templates-customizados/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Template customizado no Xcode"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"caa86984-13a5-5f45-ab4b-5581d14f14ab","previousPostId":"ad1c5a91-11cb-5a13-9137-82ce5a9e8829","nextPostId":"ffe301c1-582c-5a1d-8ad0-0583d2709746"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1344965497","2841359383"]}